metadata.name: We Grow By Koketit
metadata.description:
“If I could only see
that pain is like water
and I am like a flower
that grows and grows high
i will nor wither nor cry  
If I would only see 
that pain is like water
and I am
like a flower”

We Grow is my genesis piece here. 
It comes with a complementary Digital Canvas- a high end Videri V5 50 Inch canvas- for the lucky holder to display it.
The price of the artwork includes shipping, installation, and embedding the piece worldwide.
